KFY\" title=\"Korn Ferry\">KFY</a></span>) when I wrote about it on 6<sup>th</sup> September, as valuation has already recovered to historical average despite the macro situation</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192835/image_2155192835.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742670-korn-ferry-i-struggle-to-see-upside-potential-from-here", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 20:19:58"}, {"id": "4742675", "title": "The November Jobs Report Highlights Underlying Weakness In The Labor Market", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/838283360/image_838283360.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Close-up Of Unemployed Businessperson Carrying Cardboard Box\" data-id=\"838283360\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/838283360/image_838283360.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/838283360/image_838283360.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/838283360/image_838283360.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/838283360/image_838283360.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/838283360/image_838283360.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/838283360/image_838283360.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/838283360/image_838283360.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/838283360/image_838283360.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">RUNSTUDIO</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>November Labor Report Highlights</strong></h2> <p>Earlier today, the Bureau of Labor Statistics reported the <a href=\"https://www.bls.gov/news.release/empsit.nr0.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\">November employment report</a> for the US economy. The report indicated a better than expected 227,000 jobs increase in the month of November and a rare increase</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/838283360/image_838283360.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742675-november-jobs-report-highlights-underlying-weakness-labor-market", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 20:15:33"}, {"id": "4742667", "title": "The December FOMC Fed Meeting And How To Play It", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172781953/image_172781953.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"The US Federal Reserve building in Washington DC\" data-id=\"172781953\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"3000px\" height=\"2004px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172781953/image_172781953.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172781953/image_172781953.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172781953/image_172781953.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172781953/image_172781953.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172781953/image_172781953.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172781953/image_172781953.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172781953/image_172781953.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172781953/image_172781953.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">uschools</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>This article provides an impact assessment of the FOMC December meeting and a possible change in the Federal Funds Rate, whether it will go up, down, or stay the same, and what happens when it does.</p> <p>The chart below</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172781953/image_172781953.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742667-the-december-fomc-fed-meeting-and-how-to-play-it", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 20:08:58"}, {"id": "4742663", "title": "The Market Has Gotten Too Hot, Here's What I Would Do", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/497309419/image_497309419.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Bianca loves the fan.\" data-id=\"497309419\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/497309419/image_497309419.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/497309419/image_497309419.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/497309419/image_497309419.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/497309419/image_497309419.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/497309419/image_497309419.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/497309419/image_497309419.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/4