-choice", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 19:34:20"}, {"id": "4742558", "title": "Ladder Capital: 8% Yield And Solid Dividend Coverage Make It A Buy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/476981829/image_476981829.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"8% percentage rate icon on a white background\" data-id=\"476981829\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/476981829/image_476981829.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/476981829/image_476981829.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/476981829/image_476981829.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/476981829/image_476981829.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/476981829/image_476981829.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/476981829/image_476981829.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/476981829/image_476981829.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/476981829/image_476981829.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Supertruper</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Sir Francis Bacon once said that money is only as good as the utility that it provides. While it may be tempting to lock up money in non-income producing sources like gold and Bitcoin (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BTC-USD\" title=\"Bitcoin USD\">BTC-USD</a>), selling too early</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/476981829/image_476981829.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742558-ladder-capital-8-percent-yield-solid-dividend-coverage-make-stock-buy", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 19:30:00"}, {"id": "4742652", "title": "Integra Resources: Significant Undervaluation For This Junior Producer", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1318156166/image_1318156166.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Aerial views of Nevada Desert\" data-id=\"1318156166\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1021px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1318156166/image_1318156166.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1318156166/image_1318156166.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1318156166/image_1318156166.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1318156166/image_1318156166.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1318156166/image_1318156166.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1318156166/image_1318156166.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1318156166/image_1318156166.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1318156166/image_1318156166.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Gary Weller/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><strong>All figures are in United Stat